GDX Recon Object Variance Summary table ETL load process failed. When this process fails and sets the RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD = 99 value,IT must research to determine the root cause ASAP. If the RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD value of 99 is left in the RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD table then the corresponding truncate script will not be allowed to truncate the table and clean up old data.

,sum(REC.ADMN_DISCNT_AMT) AS INV_ADMN_DSC_AT ,sum(REC.BASE_DISCNT_AMT) AS INV_BASE_DSC_AT ,sum(REC.PRFMC_DISCNT_AMT) AS INV_PRFRM_DSC_AT ,sum(REC.FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT) AS INV_FRMLY_DSC_AT AD_CAL_PRFRM_AT ,Sum(REC.FRMLY_DISC_MTCH_AMT-REC.FRMLY_DISCNT_AMT) AS AD_CAL_FRMLY_AT ,Sum(REC.CTRC_DISC_MTCH_AMT-REC.CNTRCT_DISCNT_AMT) AS AD_CAL_CNTRC_AT ,Sum(REC.PRC_PTCT_MTCH_DISC_AMT-REC.PRC_PTCT_DISCNT_AMT) AS AD_CAL_PRCPT_AT ,SUM(REC.ADMN_DISC_DSMCH_AMT) AS DSPD_ADMN_DSC_AT ,SUM(REC.BASE_DISC_DSMCH_AMT) AS DSPD_BASE_DSC_AT ,SUM(REC.PERF_DISC_DSMCH_AMT) AS DSPD_PRFRM_DSC_AT ,SUM(REC.FRMLY_DISC_DSMCH_AMT) AS DSPD_FRMLY_DSC_AT ,SUM(REC.CTRC_DISC_DSMCH_AMT) AS DSPD_CNTRC_DSC_AT ,SUM(REC.PRC_PTCT_DSMCH_DISC_AMT) AS DSPD_PRCPT_DSC_AT ,Sum(REC.ADMN_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS DSAD_ADMN_AT ,Sum(REC.BASE_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS DSAD_BASE_AT ,Sum(REC.PERF_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS DSAD_PRFRM_AT ,Sum(REC.FRMLY_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS DSAD_FRMLY_AT ,Sum(REC.CTRC_DISC_DSADJ_AMT) AS DSAD_CNTRC_AT ,Sum(REC.PRC_PTCT_DSADJ_DISC_AMT) AS DSAD_PRCPT_AT ,Sum(REC.ADMN_PEND_DSTR_AMT) AS PNPD_ADMN_DSC_AT ,Sum(REC.BASE_PEND_DSTR_AMT) AS PNPD_BASE_DSC_AT ,Sum(REC.PERF_PEND_DSTR_AMT) AS PNPD_PRFRM_DSC_AT ,Sum(REC.FRMLY_PEND_DSTR_AMT) AS PNPD_FRMLY_DSC_AT ,Sum(REC.CTRC_PEND_DSTR_AMT) AS PNPD_CNTRC_DSC_AT ,Sum(REC.PRC_PTCT_PEND_DSTR_AMT) AS PNPD_PRCPT_DSC_AT ,Sum(REC.ADMN_PEND_ADJ_AMT) AS PNAD_ADMN_AT ,Sum(REC.BASE_PEND_ADJ_AMT) AS PNAD_BASE_AT ,Sum(REC.PERF_PEND_ADJ_AMT) AS PNAD_PRFRM_AT ,Sum(REC.FRMLY_PEND_ADJ_AMT) AS PNAD_FRMLY_AT ,Sum(REC.CTRC_PEND_ADJ_AMT) AS PNAD_CNTRC_AT ,Sum(REC.PRC_PTCT_PEND_ADJ_AMT) AS PNAD_PRCPT_AT ,COUNT(*) AS GRS_CLM_CT ,SUM(REC.CLM_TYP_CD) AS NT_CLM_CT ,SUM(REC.UQ_QTY) AS UNTS_DSPNS_QY ,SUM(CASE WHEN REC.FILE_MTCH_CNT_VL > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS PD_GRS_CLM_CT ,SUM(CASE WHEN REC.FILE_MTCH_CNT_VL > 0 THEN REC.CLM_TYP_CD ELSE 0 END) AS PD_NT_CLM_CT ,SUM(CASE WHEN REC.FILE_MTCH_CNT_VL > 0 THEN The mapping %m ran in the %s session in the %w workflow ran in %d.
GDX Recon Object Dispute Summary table ETL load process failed. When this process fails and sets the RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD = 99 value,IT must research to determine the root cause ASAP. Once the root cause is determined, the oncall must do one of two things with the Recons in error (RCNT_RECN_SUMM_QUE.RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD = 99 and RECN_SUMM_TYP_CD = 3). (1) If the records in error are simply to be rerun through this process, then have the RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD reset to 2 and restart the job in the Process Controller, or (2) if the fix is to discard the data related to the error, then reset the RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD to 199, which represents a permanent data error (TVNDR_REBT_CD.TYP_CD = 176).
If the RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD value of 99 is left in the RECN_SUMM_STAT_CD table then the corresponding truncate script will not be allowed to truncate the table and clean up old data.

%r
